      "rationale": "Experimental data from FDA benchmark study used steady-flow conditions with bovine blood at 38% hematocrit. VAD operating conditions include pulsatile components not represented in validation experiments. Temperature controlled within ±1°C of target. Achieved level 3 against required level 4 — pulsatility gap is the primary shortfall."
