      "rationale": "Hemolysis index is the primary QoI and directly maps to the clinical endpoint. Wall shear stress distribution validated at 3 of 5 operating points. Platelet activation potential, a secondary clinical QoI, was not included in the validation scope. Achieved level 3 against required level 4."
