      "rationale": "Validation performed on FDA generic pump geometry rather than the specific VAD device geometry. Steady-flow validation does not capture pulsatile hemodynamics relevant to VAD operation. Fluid properties used bovine rather than human blood rheology. Achieved level 2 against required level 4 — geometry and flow regime gaps are critical."
    },
