      "rationale": "Solver convergence monitored via residual norms but formal iterative convergence study not performed. Round-off error analysis absent. Solver error budget not separated from discretization error in reported results. Factor not formally assessed; flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
