      "rationale": "Single power-law hemolysis model (Zhang 2011) used without comparison to alternative model forms. Model form uncertainty not quantified. Alternative hemolysis constitutive relations not evaluated. Critical epistemic gap at MRL 5 — hemolysis model form is a dominant source of prediction uncertainty. Achieved level 1 against required level 5."
